{"tid":1671241,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"埋土警暴展上線啦！","createTime":"2019-10-23T10:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T18:03:40.000Z","uid":326599,"like":134,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"a84e4cb231c47ac5a66f93d06f77b65df1af6bda","tid":1671241,"uid":326599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:53:03.000Z","msg":"琴日展覽團隊聯同理大反送中關注組喺Poly M Core出面擺咗幾塊關於警察濫權嘅展板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aonmv2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faonmv2O.jpg&h=3ce17c0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LOCNrA7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLOCNrA7.jpg&h=d391d9f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾塊展板上個禮拜六日喺文化中心同中環碼頭展出過，都引起唔少遊客關注！今次嚟到Poly希望大家可以多多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個展覽除咗將呢幾個月發生嘅事整合做個紀錄之外，亦都想等啲 international students 或者身處喺平行時空嘅港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />能夠了解多啲警暴濫權，同埋侵犯人權嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n關注組嘅同學仔見琴日反應都幾好，所以依家決定加碼擺到星期五<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hmQn5RS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhmQn5RS.jpg&h=0f4ee013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期：即日起至星期五(25/10)<br />\n時間：3 - 6:30pm<br />\n地點：Poly M core對出空地<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好留喺同溫層，拗多啲fd子嚟互相交流討論下。<br />\n各位有興趣嘅話記住嚟睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d262d29655f6708774d7bb980f2abd536f5799","tid":1671241,"uid":31431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:55:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s